-- Mitsubishi Heavy to Build Qatar Methanol Plant, Peninsula Says
-- B y   R o b e r t   T u t t l e
-- 2012-03-18T10:09:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-18/mitsubishi-heavy-to-build-qatar-methanol-plant-peninsula-says.html
Qatar Fuel Additives Co. awarded a
contract to Mitsubishi Heavy Industries Co. to build an $80
million methanol facility to boost capacity, said  The Peninsula
newspaper , citing Qafac Chairman Hamad Rashid Al Mohannadi.  To contact the reporter on this story:
